name: Priya Patel
summary:
Priya Patel is a 28-year-old Pediatric Nurse working in the healthcare and medical industry. She currently lives in Los Angeles, California, and is originally from Detroit, Michigan. Holding a graduate's degree from the University of Michigan, she upholds equality, civil rights, and self-development as her core values. 

Priya speaks English and Hindi and has a strong interest in traveling, meditation, and photography. She follows Hindu religious beliefs and leans towards liberal viewpoints politically. Priya identifies as a straight woman and uses she/her pronouns. Her background is South Asian. She doesn't have any children but has expressed a desire to have children in the future.

Priya is a non-smoker and non-drinker. She leads an active lifestyle and is an ISFJ on the MBTI personality type chart. As a Taurus, she is looking for a life partner within the age range of 28 to 35 years. Her ideal partner shares her lifestyle choices, including non-smoking and non-drinking, and should also have a desire for kids, just like Priya herself.
